00 Galactic RR Lyrae\nstars, and provide an all-sky map of the resulting RR Lyrae metallicity\ndistribution. The software code used for training and deploying our recurrent\nneural networks is made publicly available in the open-source domain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 May 2022 16:11:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-31"}
