 overarching issue is the effect of the relativistic\njets on the wind, and on the structure of the emitting region in general. We\npresent results from our analysis of the optical and UV line profiles aimed to\nidentifying the wind contribution to the line emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 May 2022 18:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-31"}
